{"tid":1634174,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"點解突然聽日罷工 / 怕對家打飛機 / 多左目標 ?","createTime":"2019-10-07T06:50:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T07:13:47.000Z","uid":51555,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"4a56eed3f8591d498140b02e9fe8d340478e9028","tid":1634174,"uid":51555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T06:50:45.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">點解突然聽日要罷工?</span></div><br />\n理性啲睇,突發而自發性嘅罷工係大部份香港人眼中仲係<span style=\"color: red;\">不可能</span><br />\n因為突然而又自發嘅罷工<span style=\"color: red;\">唔可能出現</span>,又再有人會叫去<span style=\"color: violet;\">裝修党鐵</span>,從而造成<span style=\"color: orange;\">被罷工</span><br />\n流程: <br />\nStep1. 形造一個無咩可能嘅目標<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">(大三罷)</span><br />\nStep2. 同時有人提出方案<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">(裝修党鐵)</span><br />\nStep3. 好似成功達到目標<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">(被罷工)</span><br />\n疑點:<br />\n點解要提出一個<span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">可能性低嘅共同目標</span></span>,但只想<span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">依靠勇武</span></span>去達成目標?<br />\n結論:<br />\n<ins><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">只係為左引勇武落場</span></span></ins><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">點解怕對家打飛機?</span></div><br />\n當以上論點被人攻破嘅時候,再會有人入場帶風向<br />\n例如:<br />\n1. 聽日就係林奠推禁蒙面法<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">派成績表</span></span>嘅日子,點可以比佢安全咁渡過?<br />\n2. 你地唔出,聽日各大頭條就會話禁蒙面法<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">有效降低暴力事件</span></span>...<br />\n3. 對家聽日一定打曬飛機<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">多謝你地唔出黎衝</span></span><br />\n等等利用激將法去刺激手足<br />\n疑點:<br />\n我地點解要重視對家打飛機?<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><ins><span style=\"color: gold;\">其實明眼人都清楚禁蒙面法之後根本無平靜過喎</span></ins></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">絕非打擊手足士氣</div></span><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">提防假目標 切記認清事實</span></span></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">目標不可行時</span></div><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">切勿強行達成目標 引至不必要嘅損耗</span></div></span>"},{"pid":"2c414dfd57d418c51f3d681ea2ad486876c8e476","tid":1634174,"uid":51555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T06:53:40.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不論和定勇,今晚8點見</span></span>"},{"pid":"378f0f122780001de11a1c31bec866cbf0edd6a9","tid":1634174,"uid":51555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T06:58:43.000Z","msg":"推2/10"},{"pid":"5d4a8a784cfefc8eabdebf9027c853034881a0eb","tid":1634174,"uid":51555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T06:58:53.000Z","msg":"推3/10"},{"pid":"a8a494f20f0817926ee4ba6a9c2d1e5966b0b658","tid":1634174,"uid":51555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T06:59:04.000Z","msg":"推4/10"},{"pid":"9979363f0359d7b0a6565a68affcb1ffe6ac6d02","tid":1634174,"uid":51555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T06:59:17.000Z","msg":"推5/10"},{"pid":"2b2d3934493d7d57176d89e917fde505d8f7b325","tid":1634174,"uid":327740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T06:59:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"19687350568c74a70bca895afade743b2424e419","tid":1634174,"uid":159762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T06:59:21.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>香港警察濫權實錄資料庫</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tl.hkrev.info/police-timeline\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftl.hkrev.info%2Fpolice-timeline&d=fuRTyfFj%2BaUlIJflnhZSn6f05AUSLZuDOcHdeYvmXak%3D&h=5068b514\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tl.hkrev.info/police-timeline</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">仲有英文同日文版 大家落力share俾更多外國人睇！！</span>"},{"pid":"e74214000245587efed25dd55b05aa7d4b9061ca","tid":1634174,"uid":54990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T07:01:25.000Z","msg":"請起底，不推文"},{"pid":"6e2bd528e55a0c94c766f0b6de21869e39c6c978","tid":1634174,"uid":51555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T07:13:47.000Z","msg":"推爆佢"}]}